@node "Important" "IMPORTANT !!!"

    @{b}IMPORTANT NOTE@{ub}

    @{b}THIS PROGRAM CAN DESTROY YOUR MONITOR !!!@{ub}

    You shouldn't use this program if you are a @{b}beginner@{ub} on the @{b}Amiga@{ub}.
    This program can cause @{b}serious damage@{ub} to your monitor if you don't
    know what you do.
    (especially changes of "TotClk"/"TotRow")

    Please be also @{b}careful@{ub} with changes to the settings of @{b}BeamCon0@{ub}
    and appending @{b}LoadView()@{ub}.

    @{b}You have been warned !@{ub}

    I'm not responsible for any damages this program cause.
    (It shouldn't do any, of course.)

    @{b}WICHTIGE ANMERKUNG:@{ub}

    The tooltypes saved from this program version have been changed from
    previous versions.

    The program takes the tooltypes @{b}NOMMINX0@{ub} .. @{b}VIDEOMAXY0@{ub}
    and converts them to @{b}NOMMINX@{ub} .. @{b}VIDEOMAXY@{ub} ones.

    @{b}REFMODEID@{ub} becomes the value of @{b}MODEID0.@{ub}

    @{b}@{fg shine}All other overscan tooltypes are no longer used and will be deleted.@{ub}@{fg text}
@endnode

