@node "KnownBugs" "Known Bugs"

    @{b}KNOWN BUGS@{ub}

    1. @{b}VPRMinX/VPRMaxX/VPRMinY/VPRMaxY@{ub} values seems to be hardware-given.

    2. @{b}VPosX/VPosY@{ub} changes are only shown, if you click the screen to back
       and then to front again.

    3. @{b}TabCycling@{ub} doesn't work right with virtual groups.
       (MUI-Problem)

    Please read the manual to @{b}MIPrefs@{ub}, too.

    If you encounter any bugs or suspicious behaviour, contact me, and I will
    try to fix it.
    If you don't report bugs, i can't fix 'em :-)

@endnode

